------------------------------------------------------------------------------
run full test suite
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
./run_all.py            runs everything


------------------------------------------------------------------------------
prepare unit tests
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

./init.py               create some fake tree data with 10 files and many
                        useless branches which will be stripped


------------------------------------------------------------------------------
run unit tests
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

./test_SampleTree.py    run some standard tests with good and bad input data
./test_TreeCache.py     test sample cache class
./test_FileList.py      compression/decompression check of FileList
./test_BranchList.py    test class to get list of branches from cut string
./test_SampleTree_AddBranches.py    test the functionality to add new branches
                        to the output tree, filled by a TTreeFormula or a
                        (lambda) function.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
clean up
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

./clean.py              clean up all the files which have been created,
                        including test trees made by test_init.py